 FALCON EDGE CAPITAL LP Overview



												   Falcon Edge Capital Lp is a hedge fund that manages 5.1 BN dollars in regulatory AUM and has 19 employees, of which 12 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/12 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 800MM in positions, representing 16% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



