Company Overview of Falcon Edge Capital, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Falcon Edge Capital, LP is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe with a focus on global emerging markets. The firm employs long/short equity strategy to make its investments. Falcon Edge Capital, LP was founded in July 2011 and is based in New York City.


660 Madison Avenue19th FloorNew York, NY 10065United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 212-803-9080








